title: Git stash only staged changes
content: 1.Run git add \<files\>\<to\> \<stage\> 2. Run git stash push –keep-index

title: What is Interest Rate Swap
content:
IRS is a way for business/institution to swap its loan terms usually from fixed to variable rate or vice versa.
 Why it’s used? It allows companies to revise their debt conditions and to take advantage of current or expected future market conditions. In addition, it allows companies to pay lower interest rates for their loans.
